data.name: Lucid Air Dream Edition
data.description: The Lucid Air Dream Edition sets new standards for electric luxury sedans. With over 500 miles of range and 1,111 horsepower, it combines exceptional performance with unparalleled efficiency and luxury.

data.name: Hyundai IONIQ 5 Limited
data.description: The Hyundai IONIQ 5 Limited showcases the future of electric mobility with its innovative design, ultra-fast charging, and spacious interior. Built on the dedicated E-GMP platform, it offers exceptional efficiency and performance.

data.name: Ford Mustang Mach-E GT
data.description: The Ford Mustang Mach-E GT brings Mustang performance to the electric age. With its bold design and thrilling acceleration, it proves that electric can be exciting.

data.name: Mercedes-Benz EQS 450+
data.description: The Mercedes-Benz EQS 450+ represents the pinnacle of electric luxury. With its revolutionary design, advanced MBUX Hyperscreen, and exceptional range, it redefines what an electric sedan can be.

data.name: Audi e-tron GT
data.description: The Audi e-tron GT combines stunning design with exhilarating performance. This electric grand tourer delivers the perfect blend of luxury, technology, and sustainable mobility.

data.name: BMW iX xDrive50
